SUMMARY:SCRAMBLER JAM!
DTSTAMP:20260321T020253Z
DTSTART:20260325T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:SCRAMBLER JAM | 21\\+ | FREEEvery 4th Tuesday at Chop Suey we i
	nvite you to this one of a kind\, part open mic\, part open jam session\, 
	with comics in supporting roles. Full backline provided. Sign ups start at
