	:\n\nApril 3rd - 6pm - 9pm\n\n \n\nOn View:\n\nApril 3rd - April 17th\, 20
	26\n\nMon - Fri. - 10am - 4pm Sat. & Sun - 12pm - 4pm \n\nLocation: 9th Av
	e. Gallery - 2014 9th Ave\, Seattle\, WA 98121\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity
